# Nido Project Overview

This is an Astro-based web project that uses Tailwind CSS and DaisyUI for styling. The project follows Astro's standard directory structure and includes MDX support for content.

## Key Directories

- `src/pages/` - Contains all route components and pages
- `src/components/` - Reusable UI components
- `src/layouts/` - Page layouts and templates
- `src/content/` - Content collections and MDX files
- `src/styles/` - Global styles and Tailwind configuration
- `public/` - Static assets served directly

## Important Files

- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) - Astro configuration including MDX, RSS, and sitemap plugins
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [src/content.config.ts](mdc:src/content.config.ts) - Content collection configuration
- [src/consts.ts](mdc:src/consts.ts) - Project constants and configuration

## Development

The project uses the following key technologies:
- Astro v5.8.0 for the framework
- Tailwind CSS v4.1.7 for styling
- DaisyUI v5.0.37 for UI components
- MDX for content authoring

Common development commands:
- `bun run dev` - Start development server
- `bun run build` - Build for production
- `bun run preview` - Preview production build

